column5: Beautiful, bright and charming 600 Square foot guest house available for weekday and weekend rent. House includes a queen bed and sofa sleeper, kitchen, private bathroom and shower and pool use. Lots of natural light, fully heated/air-conditioned, cable tv, wifi and private entryway. Linens and dishes included. Close to Southwestern University, the Georgetown Square and only 25 miles north of Austin, TX.
column8: Beautiful, bright and cozy guesthouse available for rent
